Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission accepted!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.65,0:01:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero ended up doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.55,0:01:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He took his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.89,0:01:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,One day my Gundam will\Ndefinitely fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After staging a coup d'état...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...to overthrow the United{\i0}\N{\i1}Earth Sphere Alliance...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...OZ continues to create one{\i0}\N{\i1}disaster after another...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...in its quest to demolish{\i0}\N{\i1}the Alliance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since the Alliance has a\N{\i1}presence in every nation...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the number of casualties{\i0}\N{\i1}is expected to rise.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you've come to!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'll go get Trowa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.59,0:02:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Trowa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You should take it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Trowa, your friend's woken up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you must be hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go make some soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,With a traveling circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where I hide myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You died a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:02:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The forces retaliating against{\i0}\N{\i1}OZ have ignored our advice...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...with regards to disarmament...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and are causing unnecessary{\i0}\N{\i1}carnage around the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,One month has passed, and OZ\Nhasn't touched the colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just fighting militaristic\Nnations on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A month has passed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In OZ's eyes, you're\Nalready dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no longer restrained\Nto the colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My case isn't that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They found you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But there hasn't been one\Nmission since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What if OZ used the colonies\Nas a shield again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Or should I be following\Nyour example?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I've got\None warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts like hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I think that's probably\Nthe first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...I've heard Trowa laugh\Nout loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a favor to ask;\Nthe first since I came to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened around the world\Nwhile I was unconscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strong flap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Sally!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Explosions successful.\NWe're retreating!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all the racket?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The guerrillas, Colonel Bundt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Go after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll crush them this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In former China, within an\Nautonomous mountainous area...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...a political leader proposing\Npeace was assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He advocated demilitarization\Nand raised objections...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...to the present military.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.98,0:05:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Alliance's army targeted\Nhim in a coup d'état.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Bundt, the ringleader,\Nopposed this push for peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...and said the military\Nmust be strengthened...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...in order for the nation\Nto achieve independence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that OZ was dismembering\Nthe Alliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...civil wars were increasing\Nin such independent nations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Got them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Sally?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your first time home\Nin a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...and we've put you\Nin such danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was a huge success!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Leo, the land mobile suits!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Bundt has ordered\Nthat no one escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Found them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're climbing the slope!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That weapon's useless{\i0}\N{\i1}against suits!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can destroy its{\i0}\N{\i1}main camera!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't tell you to drop{\i0}\N{\i1}your weapons!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have you die!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I told you, it's no use!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Their back up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a Gundam!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fire!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fire! Fire!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't intend to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can beat this thing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate Nataku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a Gundam doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Weaklings like you shouldn't\Nbe fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:07:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why fight an enemy you\Ndon't stand a chance against?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's a fight we\Nmust take on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody ordered you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We're acting on our own!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You look pretty exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with us and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sally!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We know he's not an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a Gundam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll bring up the image!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a Gundam all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even OZ is having trouble\Ncontrolling those Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll return to the base!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.91,0:08:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleep well last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't need to help\Nout with getting the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm returning your favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's us that owe you a favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me that saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Nataku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nataku?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your Gundam's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Better watch what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just asking you\Nto pay for what you ate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be grateful to us\Nthat you could have this shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You want money from\Nthe soldiers who protect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you claiming\Nto protect, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All you do is stick to Bundt...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...and trample over the\Nnation's peace efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You swine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for opposing us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! You're defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's gotten into you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Wu Fei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too weak to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any right to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wu Fei...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm such a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't understand how you\Ncould call yourself a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To a man stronger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a coward who can only\Nfight those weaker than myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:11:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you're giving up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you fighting\Nfor the colonies?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,To win back peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no right to fight\Nwith Nataku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved my life yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you people are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But we won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,People join our fight because\Nwe're weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.73,0:11:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The same way you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no right to fight\Nwith Nataku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wu Fei...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,From this data, we've\Ndetermined that this area...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...is probably the guerrilla's\Nheadquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally know where\Nthey're hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But they have the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundams are incredibly\Npowerful in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If we fought it head on, it'd\Nconsiderably damage our forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Given the situation, why don't\Nwe ask for OZ's assistance...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...and stage a joint attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I disagree!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd give OZ an excuse to\Nestablish themselves in our nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What about our self-government?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to fight to alone to\Nprove ourselves to the citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still favor this idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Major Nanaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want to risk losing\Neven one of your elite soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it, but we swore\Nour lives to this nation...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...when we declared\Nindependence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We must protect our nation\Nby ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what makes us an\Nindependent nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand your determination!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll wipe out the guerrillas\Nusing our own forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,For our fatherland!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi Sally; how did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I thought that kid\Nwent with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a little fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:12:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:13:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's probably not gonna\Nleave that thing behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It would sure be great if\Nthat kid would fight with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody should be trying to force\Nhim into fighting right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's very confused now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So much was expected\Nof him during the war...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.68,0:13:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...but he couldn't deliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So now he thinks he's a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.89,0:13:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the military doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Former...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the government military!\NThey're attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Choppers have confirmed mobile{\i0}\N{\i1}suit combat missile launchers!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll fire the rocket guns then\Nsend in our mobile suit troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:13:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignore the backup firing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...and focus on the mobile suits\Nthat move in to gain control.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Helicopter unit; where's\Nthe Gundam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Locate it at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Major Nanaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We found the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam's not fighting back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll transmit the image!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a camouflage net!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The pilot's not on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Colonel Bundt!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Gundam isn't fighting{\i0}\N{\i1}back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can win this battle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The main force will join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that things are\Nnow in our favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Favorable for me, and\Nfor you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile suit troops, proceed to\Nthe Gundam to suppress it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All backup firing units!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim at the Gundam and\Nstandby to fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}Take shelter!{\i0}\N- What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Backup firing unit here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're under attack!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are OZ's Aries!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Bundt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ is staging an attack\Non our forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our forces?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Major Nanaki, OZ is{\i0}\N{\i1}part of our forces!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They sent support troops{\i0}\N{\i1}to assist us...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...in protecting our nation{\i0}\N{\i1}from the Gundam menace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But a number of soldiers were{\i0}\N{\i1}disgruntled over OZ's support...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and betrayed us to join{\i0}\N{\i1}the guerrillas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Once OZ takes over, peace\Nwill be restored to our nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe the citizens will\Nfeel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's absurd!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way the citizens{\i0}\N{\i1}would want OZ to rule!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}OZ says they'll recognize our{\i0}\N{\i1}nation's desire to self-govern.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:16:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And of course, they'll keep{\i0}\N{\i1}me on as the Head of State.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks for all your help to date,{\i0}\N{\i1}Nanaki!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Bundt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you think of anything\Nother than your own rank?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bundt's sold off this\Nnation to OZ!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happened again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A repeat of senseless wars\Nby senseless people!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,One more shot will do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hang in there!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I got hit because\NI'm weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can get them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy OZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.77,0:16:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.94,0:17:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wu Fei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wu Fei, run for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hopeless now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We can hold off the enemy\Nfor a bit, so hurry!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Sally?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey kid, why won't you\Nfight and help us?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had even half the\Nstrength you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.23,0:17:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not hurt are you kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,End it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Put an end to our misery...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wars use people's lives\Nas mere playthings...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we need\Na strong sense of faith!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sally, what're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wu Fei, you have everything\Nit takes to help save the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you never lose\Nsight of your kind heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sally; have you lost your mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've realized that\Nhealing your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...is more important\Nthan my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Sally!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wu Fei!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nataku, I've got no right\Nto pilot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But for now I'm asking you\Nto lend me your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're more or less finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We just need to secure\Nthat Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam's started moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It moved!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It crushed five Aries\Nwith ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel, that only leaves us\Nwith a couple more Aries!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them to cover our retreat!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wu Fei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Bundt is out of the picture but\NI'm sure OZ will come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.51,0:19:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...to try to take over\Nthis nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.18,0:19:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna keep\Non fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Justice...it's become such\Na cheap word now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:20:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Alliance and OZ said peace\Nand justice were their goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my own sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody has their own\Nsense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who are righteous\Nmust also have strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The weak have no right to take\Nadvantage of Nataku's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You were different this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You had the strength\Nof your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.75,0:20:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What good is strength\Nif it's not from the heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wu Fei, when you're able\Nto fight with Nataku...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...please help me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you're so weak\Nyou're still gonna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.12,0:20:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The most important thing is\Nthat my heart is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone gather around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.73,0:20:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Our next performance\Nis confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.74,0:20:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold onto your hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a request from\Nan OZ base!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.51,0:20:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,From OZ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And to celebrate I wanna\Ntry something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:21:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Something special and ex citing\Nthe OZ soldiers might enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you leave this new\Nperformance up to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you got some ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah and I think it'll be\Na big hit with the soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Trowa's usually so quiet,\Nso it must be a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You handle this, Trowa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave food and\Nthe car keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here and concentrate\Non getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everyone in my colony agreed\Nto fight using the Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam attack was started\Nby a small group...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...who felt strongly about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.32,0:21:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was one of those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with\Nacting on your emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.59,0:21:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Least that's what I was taught.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I mustn't give OZ an excuse\Nto invade the colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't rational.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So I did what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I followed my emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.47,0:21:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what you'll be\Nusing in the performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.97,0:22:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise it'll be a real blast;\Nlike nothing you've seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.01,0:22:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it the show of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.18,0:22:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It'll be my last...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.02,0:22:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...grandstand show.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.92,0:23:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of OZ's leading officers\Nare young and relentless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.32,0:23:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there no one there who\Ncan calmly interpret the war?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.69,0:23:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Their excessive military power\Nflies wildly out of control...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.19,0:23:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...resulting in one unnecessary\Nmassacre after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ begins its advancement\Ntoward outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.87,0:23:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to save the colonies,\NTrowa heads to his final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.50,0:23:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But Catherine stands before the\Nyoung man who hastens his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.51,0:23:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, on Gundam Wing, Episode 13,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.62,0:23:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"Catherine's Tears".
